  (text "TX Chain\nPower ON (no RF):\n1x BGA6130 -> 71mA\n1x QPA4263C-> 55mA\n2x LTC5507 -> 1.7mA\n2x TSV7723 -> 5mA\n\nPower ON (RF):\n1x BGA6130 -> 200mA\n1x QPA4263C-> 55mA\n2x LTC5507 -> 1.7mA\n2x TSV7723 -> 5mA\n\nPower STNDBY:\n1x BGA6130 -> 6uA\n1x QPA4263C-> 0mA\n2x LTC5507 -> 8uA\n2x TSV7723 -> 16uA\n\nSwitching speeds:\n1x BGA6130 -> 2.2us(PWRUP), 0.5us(PWRDN)\n1x QPA4263C-> To be measured\n2x LTC5507 -> 7-20us\n2x TSV7723 -> 11us\n\nTotals:\nON state(no RF):  < 133mA\nON state(RF) Linear Region:  < 262 mA\nON state(RF) Compression:  < 400 mA\nOFF state: < 30uA\nTurn on:  20 usec to output, 35 usec to measure"
    (at 352.806 210.058 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid 18ab3638-dac1-4577-892e-a20d4c842e93)
  )
  (text "RF1419D \nIL 1.6 dB\nFc = 403.5\nBW = 7.5 MHz\nThis is placed after \nthe 1st LNA to improve\nDetectivity"
    (at 172.72 111.76 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify right bottom))
    (uuid 19083743-37a0-4477-90b7-6c4597d8b3e3)
  )
  (text "RX Chain\nPower ON:\nTQP3M9036 -> 45mA\n\nPower STNDBY:\nTQP3M9036 -> 4mA\n\nSwitching speeds:\nTQP3M9036 -> 1us\n\nTotals:\nON state: < 45mA max\nOFF state: <  20uA\nSwitch ON speed: 1 usec\nSwitch OFF speed: 1 usec"
    (at 353.568 76.962 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid 4038477b-9dac-442e-9f28-e8a6f1ccf1e5)
  )
